examples.en: I'm not overly fond of cooking.
I'm not overly fond of cats.
You cannot be overly cautious when you're driving in snow.
They felt the waiter was being overly familiar.
Your views on economics are overly simplistic.
The novel disappoints by being predictable and overly long.
His overly lax managerial style has resulted in a department that is slothful and unproductive.
The political party was discountenanced by the actions of a few of its overly zealous members.
